name: Reporting requirement Care homes; liability; insurance; coverage (repealed July 1, 2014). L 2013, c 212, 2.
text: Reporting requirement.  The department shall submit an annual report to the legislature, no later than twenty days prior to the convening of each regular session, on the status, efficacy, and any other relevant information regarding the young adult voluntary foster care program established by this part. [L 2013, c 252, pt of §2]
